# Project Rules

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Django templated SSR
- Backend: Django, with a Sqlite3 DB
- Styling: Fomantic/Semantic UI CSS
- Static assets: placed in `/static`, and swept into the directory to be served by `uv run manage.py collectstatic`

## Run notes, important

- when running Python, always use `uv`.  e.g.: `uv run pytest` or `uv run manage.py runserver`

## Code Standards

- Use type hints where possible in Python code
- Prefer built-in Django utilities where possible
- Use standard Django file paths